The Covid-19 coronavirus disease has swiftly spread around the world since it was first detected in December.
From travel bans to social distancing to shelter-in-place orders and school and office closures, the virus has impacted millions of lives.
How do I deal with social distancing and its impact on my relationships?
This Vox guide will answer your questions and help you navigate society’s new normal.
